question: Which of the following teams has won the 2017 Kalpathi AGS - Buchi Babu All-India Invitation cricket tournament?
explanation: The Hyderabad team have won the 2017 Kalpathi AGS - Buchi Babu All-India Invitation cricket tournament. In the final at Chennai on September 15, they defeated TNCA President\'s XI by 8 wickets.
